org.dotplot.tokenizer
Interface ITokenFilter

All Superinterfaces:
ITokenStream
All Known Implementing Classes:
BaseTokenFilter, KeyWordFilter
public interface ITokenFilter
extends ITokenStream

Interface for a Tokenfilter.

A Tokenfilter filters several token out of a token stream and returns the next unfiltered token.
